name: David Walker
description: I’m honest, easy going, helpful, open minded, ready to start a relationship, grow it, and time will tell. I like to share my values with honest people. I am someone who has been described as a mild extrovert-person who enjoys to be cuddled at but is somewhat reserved, on the quiet side I definitely appreciate life in general.I would like to meet someone with the same morals and values that I have. Someone honest, with integrity, manners and common sense.
